sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant K as Keycloak
    participant B as Backend
    
    U->>F: Access Protected Route
    F->>F: Check Token
    F->>|No Token| K: Redirect to Login
    K->>U: Show Login Form
    U->>K: Enter Credentials
    K->>K: Authenticate
    K->>F: Return JWT Token
    F->>F: Store Token
    F->>B: API Request + Token
    B->>K: Validate Token
    K->>B: Token Valid + User Info
    B->>B: Extract Roles
    B->>B: Check @PreAuthorize
    B->>|Authorized| F: Return Data
    B->>|Unauthorized| F: 403 Forbidden
    F->>U: Display Content

